Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
hello looking for an account manager

Thanks for your interest! At this time, dedicated account management is reserved for advertisers who meet a daily spend threshold of $1,000 or more. If you’re not at that level yet, no worries — our self-serve platform has everything you need to launch and optimize your campaigns successfully. Our support team is also available via chat or email if you need any help. In the meantime, feel free to check out our Help Center — it’s a great resource for quick answers if you don’t need to reach out to support directly. And don’t forget to subscribe to our email updates and keep an eye out for our monthly webinar training sessions! Let us know if you’d like assistance getting started.
looking for inspiration for ads for newsbreak?

To get inspired for your NewsBreak ads, you can explore successful ad campaigns in similar industries or check out our Help Center for tips on creating effective ads. Consider focusing on engaging visuals, clear messaging, and targeting the right audience to maximize your ad's impact. If you have any specific questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
where do i check out the ads in similar industries?

While we don't have a specific platform to view ads from similar industries directly, you can explore industry reports, marketing blogs, or case studies online for insights. Additionally, platforms like Facebook Ad Library or Google Ads Gallery can provide examples of ads across various industries. If you need more tailored advice for NewsBreak, feel free to ask!
